## ğŸ“– About the App  
Kanban-Board is designed to help users securely log in and manage their tasks in an organized **Kanban-style workflow**.  

**Features:**  
ğŸ“Œ **User Authentication** â€“ Secure login with JSON Web Tokens (JWT).  
ğŸ“Œ **Task Management** â€“ Users can view, create, and edit tasks.  
ğŸ“Œ **Drag & Drop** â€“ Move tasks across columns (TODO, In Progress, Done).  
ğŸ“Œ **Persistent Data** â€“ Tasks and user info are stored in a PostgreSQL database.  
ğŸ“Œ **Session Handling** â€“ Tokens expire after inactivity to ensure security.  

